lead_paragraph: Five times a world champion but without a single medal from three previous Olympics, Hungary's Katinka Hosszu finally struck gold on Saturday and demolished the 400 meters individual medley world record as well.

headline.print_headline: Swimming: Hungary's Iron Lady Finally Strikes Gold
